{
  "stem": "1895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They found that they still had some room on the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so early in the morning, they went down to the other ghetto, to Walowa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they started a selection procedure in Walowa and they took about 2,500 people from Walowa that day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that first day, on August 5th, they took  10,000 Jews from Glinice and about 2,500 Jews from Walowa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was called-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was one of these deportations or  re-settlement actions, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we came back that morning from my job at the munitions factory, I came face to face with a group of Jews that were taken out from the 2,500 who were taken out from the ghetto and marched to the railroad station, because the munitions factory was located near the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we actually-- when they brought us back to the ghetto, we actually came face to face with the people that were being taken out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is when I witnessed the first thing-- the first time a so-called deportation or re-settlement action.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's very difficult for me to describe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we came on a large meadow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a large field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All this was taking place in the outskirts of the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They never took people through the main streets of the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They always took the people-- even though it was a longer route, they took them out of the-- out of sight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in a-- in a large, empty field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came across [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] these columns of people that were being taken out from Walowa.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
